# Walkthrough - Remove #tags Feature (UI Only)

I have removed the "Tags" input field from the daily journal entry screen ("Today" tab).

## Changes

### User Interface
- **Today Screen**: Removed the "Tags (comma separated)" text input field from the "Wrap Up" page.
- **Cleaned Up**: Removed unused `_tagsController` and associated logic.

### Data & functionality
- **Preserved**: Existing tags in your journal history are preserved.
- **Preserved**: Weekly keyword analysis still uses tags if they exist in past entries.
- **Preserved**: Search functionality still allows finding old entries by their tags.
- **New Entries**: New entries will simply have no tags saved.

